title: Mirror cover

claims.preamble: I claim the ornamental design for a mirror cover, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front perspective view of the design of the present invention for a mirror cover;
FIG. 2 is a rear perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a rear elevation view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a left side elevation view thereof, the right side elevation view being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 6 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a bottom plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 8 is a perspective view thereof in a relaxed state.
The features of the mirror cover shown in broken lines are for illustrative purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
